In [34]:
def model_train_test_cereals(Model):
    model = Model()
    model.fit(ip_train, op_train)
    train_pred = model.predict(ip_train)
    test_pred = model.predict(ip_test)
    train_MSE = mean_squared_error(train_pred, op_train)
    train_MAE = mean_absolute_error(train_pred, op_train)
    test_MSE = mean_absolute_error(test_pred, op_test)
    test_MAE = mean_absolute_error(test_pred, op_test)
    return(train_MSE,train_MAE,test_MSE,test_MAE)
